{
  "stem": "6258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somehow, I don't know, it was maybe to us not good, but it was unconceivable that we should part and be different.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then even to endanger other people, not to mention that our-- at this time, well, financial situation was not that good.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So parents didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Besides, as many people, my parents thought that this war could not be so different than the First World War.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "During First World War, front was front and armies were armies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in-- there was nothing war against woman, against children, against older people, and against civilian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And during First World War, the universities were open and everything was still going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this war was different, very different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at the end of November and the end of December.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very first glimpse of them, it was when we were crossing-- first of all, we saw the German--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, when they entered, actually?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, but-- well, when we were crossing the rivers and coming from east Poland to-- to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I noticed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ghetto was set up in 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "March.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember this exact.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was about two months or three months earlier that the Jews should go to-- to-- it will be ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, but it was, first we were getting Kennkarted, the IDs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to register, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kennkarte.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kenn, it means-- well, like ID.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Karte, it was large like this, with photograph.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have photograph from-- from that Kennkarte.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to register.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while this registration, for some strange reason-- and nobody knew why and why not-- some people got permission to stay in Krakow and some absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all the people who did not get this Kennkarte can move outside of Krakow and settle in some suburbs there.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
